$Id$

	iperfc


iperfc [iperf control program/daemon]

It is organized as follows:

config/		holds autoconf junk.
I2util/		convienient utility functions... Error reporting, hash funcs...
ipcntrl		directory for api - a high level abstraction for
		speaking the iperfc protocol.
iperfcd/	An owamp server implementation.
iperfc/		A command line iperfc client. (Takes *most* iperf args.)
piperfc/	A client-daemon for continuous tests.
